  </ol>
  <p style="margin-left: 42.55pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif';">Tất cả c&aacute;c tổ chức, c&ocirc;ng ty, c&aacute; nh&acirc;n trong v&agrave; ngo&agrave;i nước c&oacute; giấy ph&eacute;p kinh doanh theo luật ph&aacute;p Việt Nam v&agrave; c&oacute; nguồn t&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh ph&ugrave; hợp để t&agrave;i trợ cho Dự &aacute;n Black and White.</span></p>
  <ol start="2">
  <li style="text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'Monotype Corsiva'; color: #7030a0;">L&agrave;m th</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: #7030a0;">ế</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'Monotype Corsiva'; color: #7030a0;"> n&agrave;o đ</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: #7030a0;">ể</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'Monotype Corsiva'; color: #7030a0;"> t&agrave;i tr</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: #7030a0;">ợ</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'Monotype Corsiva'; color: #7030a0;">?</span></strong></li>
